  "1834980": {
    "name": "祭典之夜",
    "steam_appid": 1834980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/b3e14a26b87d88da25a3046d130e23b3.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/b3e14a26b87d88da25a3046d130e23b3.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/b3e14a26b87d88da25a3046d130e23b3.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与4-8名小伙伴（或是即将成为小伙伴的朋友们）一起加入神秘的祭典派对，齐心协力只为至上的目标：<strong>召唤克苏鲁</strong>！<br>至少... 如果你是蛋蛋怪的话...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欺骗你的伙伴们</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/38dfa4405c914f07044df0a38bde92d6.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/38dfa4405c914f07044df0a38bde92d6.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/38dfa4405c914f07044df0a38bde92d6.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>人类特工们听令：是时候展现你们的技术了！用尽一切手段搅乱派对：撒谎，隐瞒，破坏，制造越多的混乱越好！记住：朋友没了还能再交，但偷取祭典原液，倒卖古神魔法，这可是千载难逢的商机啊！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逆天改命</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/d848d6d5c0b59885f1f9f2f5ff55c7d7.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/d848d6d5c0b59885f1f9f2f5ff55c7d7.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/d848d6d5c0b59885f1f9f2f5ff55c7d7.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“<i>哎呀我不会骗人玩不了狼人杀类游戏怎么办呀...</i>”<br>不要担心！被打晕了或是被打入了大牢？利用你的花言巧语说服其他玩家让他们来帮你！祭典之夜中没有任何前期玩家死亡状态，所有人全程都会参与其中，又好看又好玩。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>乱中取精</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/291afc061b75cbee0030541fe1d9be47.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/291afc061b75cbee0030541fe1d9be47.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/291afc061b75cbee0030541fe1d9be47.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>祭典之夜中，隐藏身份玩家首要目的为巧妙地制造混乱与混淆视听，而不是单一地击杀其他玩家。情报存在于闭环之中，怪物们需要慢慢积累而不是担心被击杀时情报流失。<br><br>游戏中没有会不小心直接暴露重要情报的状况。哪怕隐藏身份玩家中有一人提前暴露，其本人与队友仍有许多可利用的策略来混淆其他玩家并将嫌疑推卸给他人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>肉鸽、地图种子、随机性</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/65dffdf83a9263d846d3c241475cb3d0.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/65dffdf83a9263d846d3c241475cb3d0.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/65dffdf83a9263d846d3c241475cb3d0.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>祭典之夜将肉鸽元素融入推理类游戏。基于每轮玩家祭典完成情况，新的物品与地图元素会随机变换，给人怪双方提供更多可用助于推理的道具！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>古神降临</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/ae73122dc554073aedc7a20e402aee36.poster.avif?t=1732128657\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/ae73122dc554073aedc7a20e402aee36.webm?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834980/extras/ae73122dc554073aedc7a20e402aee36.mp4?t=1732128657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>加入对无尽恐惧深渊的探索，寻找世界各地的祭典圣地，解锁古神与黄金之屋的秘密关联... 随着时间推移，一切尽会全盘托出！<br><br>在那之前？好好享受祭典派对吧！",
